I worked around this by replacing my ===== lines with -------- lines.

Note that you cannot exclude the possibility that legit code contains things like ======= or <<<<<<< so whatever regex the hook is using at the moment should probably be made more stringent in order to avoid these false positives.

Thanks,

H.


